## Getting an API Key

1. Visit [OpenRouter](https://openrouter.ai/) to register an account
2. Go to the [Keys page](https://openrouter.ai/keys) to create an API Key
3. Format: `sk-or-v1-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx`
4. Free models can be used without deposit

